# Crash frontend env -- LOCAL ONLY. Copy to .env and fill in. .env is gitignored; NEVER commit a key.
#
# GMI / Phinite inference tester key (demo). The "Test Agent / Test Skill" demo flow uses this to
# make a REAL inference call to Phinite AI via GMI's OpenAI-compatible endpoint (api.gmi-serving.com).
# Everything else in that flow (the x402/USDC settlement, the Phinite orchestration trace) is simulated
# for the demo; only the inference is live. If this is empty, the flow falls back to a canned response.
VITE_GMI_API_KEY=
